# vu-meter

VU-Meter build on Atmega32 - simple code written in atmel assembler. 

VU meter is a part of audio mixer project build as modular construction allowing 
build a simple mixer and expand it depending on your needs. VU meter is stereo
display showing current value of signal (using bar of lights) as well as the peak 
value displayed on single led. 

Schematic and pcb design one can find in attached .png files. 

